      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this fantastic find! This vehicle is in truly good condition, having been well-maintained and cared for throughout its life. It runs smoothly and looks great, showing only the minor, expected signs of careful use. It\u2019s a reliable, high-quality ride that's perfect for anyone looking for a dependable car that still has plenty of great miles ahead!",
