    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously maintained to the highest standard. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and no imperfections to speak of. Inside, the cabin is pristine, with leather that looks and feels brand new. Every feature and electronic component functions perfectly, and the engine performs exactly as it did the day it left the factory. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been kept in such impeccable state.",
      "price": 48000.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
